
See the requirements: https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Steam#Installation

* enable multilib: https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Official_repositories#multilib

* install steam

sudo pacman -S steam

* install stuff:

sudo pacman -S lib32-nvidia-utils libvdpau-va-gl lib32-libvdpau

lib32-nvidia-utils: https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Xorg#Driver_installation
libvdpau-va-gl lib32-libvdpau: https://www.reddit.com/r/ManjaroLinux/comments/7jvu8i/you_are_missing_the_following_32bit_libraries_and/drb1mbn/

---

See also this for potentially missing libraries: https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Steam/Troubleshooting#Debugging_shared_libraries
